{"tid":1695233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布 下星期三13/10全港三罷","createTime":"2019-11-05T13:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:50:31.000Z","uid":67904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"530ed9faf9e02cb2752d7f83facb55366fe74081","tid":1695233,"uid":67904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:43:06.000Z","msg":"周同學，建仔，爆眼女仔同記者仲有無數死傷者<br />\n義士唔係condom<br />\n<br />\n本人以連登呢個平台宣布<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下星期三13/10全港三罷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下星期三13/10全港三罷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n比一個星期大家宣傳同準備，攞返8月5嘅氣勢<br />\n香港人怕死我無辦法，以死革命我哋未必做到<br />\n但係三罷將會集合所有香港人嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動將會喺當日進行，令全民三罷更加順利<br />\n<br />\n請文宣組開工製作文宣<br />\n<br />\nFacebook,airdrop,IG開去"},{"pid":"d53aae23097e735056fa20cf900185510214eb00","tid":1695233,"uid":67904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"全民三罷，動用自己最大嘅影響力"},{"pid":"eb51b327e26fe9f9323339215aa752e867a08b7f","tid":1695233,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:44:37.000Z","msg":"13/10?"},{"pid":"260670bbdfe0f01a95c24c6fc3494d29d45f5d61","tid":1695233,"uid":67904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb51b327e26fe9f9323339215aa752e867a08b7f","tid":1695233,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:44:37.000Z","msg":"13/10?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"打錯  開過"},{"pid":"dc3df7f6a31a3dfd4a5f639b1bb194fb656275eb","tid":1695233,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"13/11呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開過啦"},{"pid":"080d72e7e9ea406e219cab5664832cb05c4fa317","tid":1695233,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:45:37.000Z","msg":"冇諗到一場反修例運動可以出到咁多金句出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https: